      <title>巴西警方建议对前总统博索纳罗提起政变指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/brazil-police-to-recommend-charges-against-ex-president-bolsonaro-in-coup-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士透露，巴西联邦警察在调查涉嫌政变企图后，将建议对前总统雅伊尔·博索纳罗提起刑事指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/brazil-police-to-recommend-charges-against-ex-president-bolsonaro-in-coup-probe</guid>
